	<name>Hibersap</name>
	<description>
		Hibersap is a small framework that offers an abstraction layer
		on top of the SAP Java Connector (JCo). It maps Java classes to
		SAP function modules using Java Annotations and reduces the
		technical code to call a function in a SAP back-end system to a
		minimum. Hibersap's API is very similar to Hibernate, thus
		offering a familiar programming interface to developers.
	</description>
